  <description><![CDATA[<p>Set in a scenic and peaceful location facing the jagged peaks of the Lizard Range along the banks of the Elk River, the Stanford Resort is one of Fernie's finest hotels. It offers an array of amenities including the locals' favourite Indian restaurant, and focuses on the individual guest experience whilst representing excellent value. Both the ski bus and resort shuttle stop at the hotel to take you to the ski area or to downtown Fernie.</p>]]></description>
